   "source": [
    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Custom Tokenizer Comparison Lab\\n\",\"**NLP Project 11 of 100**\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Project Overview\\n\",\"Compare tokenization strategies: whitespace, regex, spaCy, and Hugging Face transformer tokenizers. Understand how tokenization affects downstream NLP tasks.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Learning Objectives\\n\",\"1. Understand different tokenization approaches and their trade-offs.\\n\",\"2. Measure vocabulary size, OOV rate, and token count per approach.\\n\",\"3. See how tokenization affects classification performance.\\n\",\"4. Learn about subword tokenization (BPE, WordPiece, Unigram).\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Problem Statement\\n\",\"Tokenization is the first step in any NLP pipeline. Different strategies produce different tokens, affecting model performance.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Why This Matters\\n\",\"- Wrong tokenization can lose important information.\\n\",\"- Subword tokenizers handle rare words better than word-level ones.\\n\",\"- Understanding tokenization helps debug NLP model failures.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Dataset Overview\\n\",\"We use a sample of news text to compare tokenizers.\\n\",\"## Dataset Source: AG News from Hugging Face (sample).\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import subprocess, sys, importlib\\nfor pkg in [\\\"pandas\\\",\\\"numpy\\\",\\\"matplotlib\\\",\\\"seaborn\\\",\\\"scikit-learn\\\",\\\"spacy\\\",\\\"transformers\\\",\\\"datasets\\\"]:\\n    try: importlib.import_module(pkg.replace('-','_'))\\n    except ImportError: subprocess.check_call([sys.executable,\\\"-m\\\",\\\"pip\\\",\\\"install\\\",\\\"-q\\\",pkg])\\ntry:\\n    import spacy; spacy.load('en_core_web_sm')\\nexcept: subprocess.check_call([sys.executable,\\\"-m\\\",\\\"spacy\\\",\\\"download\\\",\\\"en_core_web_sm\\\"])\\nprint('Environment ready.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd, matplotlib.pyplot as plt, seaborn as sns, re\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nsns.set_style('whitegrid')\\n%matplotlib inline\\nprint('Imports loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"SEED = 42; N_SAMPLES = 500\\nnp.random.seed(SEED)\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Dataset Loading\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"from datasets import load_dataset\\nds = load_dataset('fancyzhx/ag_news', split='train')\\ndf = ds.to_pandas().sample(n=N_SAMPLES, random_state=SEED).reset_index(drop=True)\\ntexts = df['text'].tolist()\\nprint(f'Loaded {len(texts)} texts'); print(texts[0][:200])\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Tokenizer Implementations\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"# 1. Whitespace tokenizer\\ndef whitespace_tokenize(text): return text.split()\\n\\n# 2. Regex tokenizer\\ndef regex_tokenize(text): return re.findall(r'\\\\b\\\\w+\\\\b', text.lower())\\n\\n# 3. spaCy tokenizer\\nimport spacy\\nnlp = spacy.load('en_core_web_sm', disable=['ner','parser','tagger'])\\ndef spacy_tokenize(text): return [t.text for t in nlp(text)]\\n\\n# 4. Transformer tokenizer (WordPiece)\\nfrom transformers import AutoTokenizer\\nbert_tok = AutoTokenizer.from_pretrained('distilbert-base-uncased')\\ndef transformer_tokenize(text): return bert_tok.tokenize(text)\\n\\nTOKENIZERS = {'Whitespace': whitespace_tokenize, 'Regex': regex_tokenize,\\n              'spaCy': spacy_tokenize, 'WordPiece (BERT)': transformer_tokenize}\\nprint('Tokenizers ready.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Comparison Analysis\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"results = []\\nfor name, tok_fn in TOKENIZERS.items():\\n    all_tokens = [tok_fn(t) for t in texts]\\n    flat = [t for tokens in all_tokens for t in tokens]\\n    vocab = set(flat)\\n    avg_len = np.mean([len(t) for t in all_tokens])\\n    results.append({'Tokenizer': name, 'Vocab Size': len(vocab),\\n                    'Avg Tokens/Doc': round(avg_len, 1), 'Total Tokens': len(flat)})\\n\\nresults_df = pd.DataFrame(results)\\nprint(results_df.to_string(index=False))\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(12, 5))\\nresults_df.plot(x='Tokenizer', y='Vocab Size', kind='bar', ax=axes[0], color='steelblue', legend=False)\\naxes[0].set_title('Vocabulary Size by Tokenizer'); axes[0].tick_params(axis='x', rotation=30)\\nresults_df.plot(x='Tokenizer', y='Avg Tokens/Doc', kind='bar', ax=axes[1], color='coral', legend=False)\\naxes[1].set_title('Avg Tokens per Document'); axes[1].tick_params(axis='x', rotation=30)\\nplt.tight_layout(); plt.show()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Example Comparison\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"sample = texts[0][:100]\\nprint(f'Text: {sample}\\\\n')\\nfor name, tok_fn in TOKENIZERS.items():\\n    tokens = tok_fn(sample)\\n    print(f'{name:20s} ({len(tokens):2d} tokens): {tokens[:15]}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Key Insights\\n\",\"1. **Whitespace is simplest** but doesn't handle punctuation well.\\n\",\"2. **Regex is better** — strips punctuation and normalizes case.\\n\",\"3. **spaCy handles edge cases** (contractions, hyphens) correctly.\\n\",\"4. **WordPiece creates more tokens** but has a fixed, smaller vocabulary — handles any word.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Limitations\\n\",\"- Comparison on English only.\\n\",\"- Doesn't measure downstream task impact directly.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Tokenization choice significantly affects NLP pipelines.**\\n\",\"- **Subword tokenizers (BPE/WordPiece) eliminate OOV problems.**\\n\",\"- **spaCy offers the best balance for traditional NLP pipelines.**\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
    " \"metadata\":{\"kernelspec\":{\"display_name\":\"Python 3\",\"language\":\"python\",\"name\":\"python3\"},\"language_info\":{\"name\":\"python\",\"version\":\"3.11.0\"}},\n",
    " \"nbformat\":4,\"nbformat_minor\":5\n",
    "}\n"
